{"tid":1157822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳浩天要求美國取消香港關係法 踢香港出wto 焦土香港","createTime":"2019-05-16T14:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T20:02:19.000Z","uid":133680,"like":59,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"061871061e918dfec7208aa4945986ea863de111","tid":1157822,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:15:22.000Z","msg":"香港民族黨召集人陳浩天昨日向美國總統川普發公開信，促請川普重新審視《美國&mdash;香港政策法》，並撤銷香港及中國作為世界貿易組織（WTO）成員身分。商務及經濟發展局表示，譴責任何人破壞香港經貿利益，強調香港現時的地位得來不易；有民主派人士指港府必須凸顯香港並非內地普通城市，才是保住世貿成員身分方法。<br />\n<br />\n明報報導，陳浩天將信件上載至民族黨臉書（facebook）專頁及推特（Twitter）。陳浩天在信中稱港府是順從中央政府的傀儡，沒有在世貿行使自己作為成員的權利，只會為中國在世貿上提供多一個席位及投票權，屬無理及不公平。他又提到早前香港外國記者會（FCC）邀請他在午餐會上演講，但遭香港及中央政府施壓及公開反對，意圖強迫對方取消活動。"},{"pid":"765d084366bbd1850c4548538f1483868b5a96a6","tid":1157822,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee75b2a8e3176b81c12b962299acaadc7f7a3f25","tid":1157822,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:21:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c740dd9bad42249c10430edd436afa1ec249b00","tid":1157822,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:25:11.000Z","msg":"焦土又贏。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a019702bd2de9969e22e566a13c27382f077a4ee","tid":1157822,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c740dd9bad42249c10430edd436afa1ec249b00","tid":1157822,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:25:11.000Z","msg":"焦土又贏。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:26:00.000Z","msg":"教主「我講吓咋wo」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.